data.description: A rare find in today's inventory; move in ready 4 bedroom/2 bath home within city limits under 200,000.  Owners have completed renovations in every room:  converted garage to 4th bedroom; new water heater and dishwasher; new light fixtures and ceiling fans; new hardware on doors and cabinets; new blinds; new carpet in common area; added an additional source of heat in the event it was needed;  fresh paint throughout the home; new bathroom vanities in bathrooms; new microwave; new motion detector and so much more.  In addition to the interior upgrades - the backyard has been fenced including specialty gates for entrance and exit plus a storage shed for the buyer's storage needs.  Additional information upon request.
